<objective>
Fix campaign cell capacity leak in finalizeCampaign (BUG-02).

Purpose: Currently, when a campaign is finalized, the campaign cell may contain excess capacity (from pledges that were already processed). This excess stays with the cell and flows to whoever triggers finalization (the finalizer). By design, excess capacity should return to the creator.

Output: finalizeCampaign now creates two outputs: the finalized campaign cell (minimum capacity) and a change output routing excess capacity back to the creator's lock script.
</objective>

