- finalizeCampaign creates one output: the finalized campaign cell
- Campaign cell capacity = minimum required (data size + base overhead)
- Original campaign cell may have had excess capacity (from pledges), which disappears from creator's custody
- Whoever signs the finalize transaction (finalizer) retains that excess capacity in fee optimization
